::::{.g-col-1 .card .card-body .text-center}
#### Virtual Gateway Workshop {.card-title}

Just getting started in education research, or curious about what PEER is like? Join us for a 90-minute virtual gateway workshop on October 5, 4:30-6:00 eastern time.

:::{more-info-button}
[More Information](schools/virtual-gateway/index.qmd){.btn role="button" .btn-primary .rounded-pill}
:::

